Body: Description: Requesting an offline patch for version 5.9.4.1 as the live update isn't downloading it.
What We've Learned Updated: Customer needs offline patch to upgrade to 5941

Next Steps Updated: Waiting for 5941 offline patch to be released. In the meantime, asked customer if they can make an exception and allow internet connection to their EPP server so we can upgrade it using Live Update.

What We've Learned Updated: Port 80 may be blocked and that is why live update doesn't work.

Customer needs offline patch to upgrade to 5941

Next Steps Updated: 29Jan: Asked customer to check internally with their colleagues if the live update port(80) is blocked.

Waiting for 5941 offline patch to be released. In the meantime, asked customer if they can make an exception and allow internet connection to their EPP server so we can upgrade it using Live Update.
